description: The field contains aggregated scores for the altenative factors
The field contains aggregated scores for the sentiment related factors
The field indicates how strong the growth factor effects on the stock
The field shows whether price momentum or price reversion factor is influencing the stock price
The financially strong companies get quality scores
Score is the sum of the sentiment, quality, value, growth, price momentum and reversion, alternative and tree factors
Tree aggregates the trained machine learning model non-linear components into a score
Value contains the aggregated score whether the company is relatively over or underpriced
